<dim:field element="description" qualifier="abstract" language="en" mdschema="dc">This dataset contains the location of all currently operational Whisky distilleries in Scotland. In addition to the geolocation information, the dataset contains information on the nature of the whisky giving a score for body, sweetness, smoky, medicinal, tabacco, honey, Spicy, Winey, nutty, malty, fruity, floral nature of each distillery. Only one score per distillery is provided to it is assumed that this is a generalisation of the whisky that each distillery offers.</dim:field>
